	0 0 rlineto} for
	stroke
} for
-1.62 inch 1.3 inch moveto
(D) show
grestore


gsave
2.5 inch 0 inch translate
-1.6 inch 0.4 inch moveto
/Times-Roman findfont
12 scalefont setfont
((a)) show
grestore


grestore



